descriptionHtml:
[size=5]Tools:[/size]
[size=2]SKSE: http://skse.silverlock.org/[/size]
[size=2]SkyUI: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863/?[/size]
[size=2]RaceMenu Mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624//?[/size]
[size=2]ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?[/size]
[size=2]Head: Bald Head: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11140/?[/size]
[size=2]Brows: Brows http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?[/size]
[size=2]Eyes: The Eyes Of Beauty http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?[/size]
[size=2]Scars: Northborn Scars: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49279/?[/size]

[color=#0000ff][size=4]Follow these steps:[/size][/color]

[size=2]1. Download my mod and install it at data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets[/size]
[size=2]2. Open Skyrim using SKSE[/size]
[size=2]3. Load any working save file[/size]
[size=2]4. Open the console[/size]
[size=2]5. Type showracemenu[/size]
[size=2]6. Select the Nord Race[/size]
[size=2]7. Look for the slide option "preset slot"[/size]
[size=2]8. Press F9 and done[/size]
author: RolloTheBerserker
